ws.rocket.path.support

Class SampleAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • ws.rocket.path.support.SampleAlgorithm

  • public final class SampleAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
    Sample algorithms for delivery of HTTP requests to objects and then handling the response view from the object. This class should not be used in a production code: it is only meant to be taken as an example, API users may copy code from here to use in their application and refine it as needed.

    This class is marked final and API users should also mark their algorithm implementation class final (no need for sub-classing).
